###Mean Scores for self-efficacy for using Multiple Document Literacy and Argumentative Thinking skills, pre- and posttest.
COMPUTE SWK1MDLAll = (SWK1MDL_SQ001 + SWK1MDL_SQ002 + SWK1MDL_SQ003 + SWK1MDL_SQ004 + SWK1MDL_SQ005 + SWK1MDL_SQ006)/6.
COMPUTE SWK1ADAll = (SWK1AD_SQ001 + SWK1AD_SQ002 + SWK1AD_SQ003 + SWK1AD_SQ004 + SWK1AD_SQ005 + SWK1AD_SQ006)/6.
COMPUTE SWK2MDLAll = (SWK2MDL_SQ001 + SWK2MDL_SQ002 + SWK2MDL_SQ003 + SWK2MDL_SQ004 + SWK2MDL_SQ005 + SWK2MDL_SQ006)/6.
COMPUTE SWK2ADAll = (SWK2AD_SQ001 + SWK2AD_SQ002 + SWK2AD_SQ003 + SWK2AD_SQ004 + SWK2AD_SQ005 + SWK2AD_SQ006)/6.

###Average Scores for self-efficacy pre- and posttest.
COMPUTE SWK1_All=(SWK1MDLAll + SWK1ADAll)/2.
COMPUTE SWK2_All=(SWK2MDLAll + SWK2ADAll)/2.


